      "content": "but i feel like 1200mg isn't much for such bad pain. if i take one 400mg pill every 2 hours, im only at 4800mg after a full day, but i'll probably sleep after 10 hours anyway. wouldn't it be better to just stay ahead of the inflammation so i don't have to suffer through the spikes? it seems more efficient that way.",
